# Model

The structure of our model is
$$
\mbox{fuel consumption} 
=  
\mbox{slope} \times \mbox{vehicle weight} + \mbox{intercept}
$$
where 

  - the fuel consumption is measured in liters per 100 km and 
  - the vehicle weight is given in kg.

